The '''Hot Pepper''' is a [[Fruits|fruit]] [[Crops|crop]] that grows from [[Pepper Seeds]] after 5 days.

==Stages==
When harvested, each Hot Pepper plant gives 1 Hot Pepper every 3 days, with a 3% chance for more Hot Peppers.
