==Tailoring==
Hot Pepper is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a dyeable {{name|Shorts|link=Tailoring#Pants{{!}}Shorts|class=inline}}. It is a red dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the red dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]], for use in [[dyeing]].

==Quests==
*[[George]] requests a Hot Pepper by mail on the 25th of [[Summer]] in the [[Quests#Knee Therapy|"Knee Therapy" Quest]].  The reward is {{Price|200}} and 1 [[Friendship]] heart.
*Hot Pepper may be randomly requested in [[Summer]] at the [[Quests#Help Wanted Quests|"Help Wanted" board]] outside [[Pierre's General Store]] for a reward of {{Price|120}} and 150 [[Friendship]] points.

